# Infra & CI/CD Rules

## Auto Wiring
- CDK must supply every Lambda with:
  - Custom domains
  - Runtime API URL
  - Admin API URL
  - Vendor API URL
  - Bedrock agent/alias IDs
  - JWT issuer/audience

## Pipelines
- Migrate DB via Alembic before deploying lambdas.
- Strict: no manual copying of ARNs, IDs, URLs.
- All env must derive from CDK outputs & SSM/Secrets Manager.

## Stacks
- Core stacks:
  - DataPlaneStack
  - RuntimeApiStack
  - PortalStack
